<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chess Hive</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Archivo+Black&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/primary_styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Chess Hive</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/" onclick="event.preventDefault();">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login">Join Community</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contactus">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="secondary-header">Bringing Chess Passionates from Campuses to the Board</div>
    
    <main>
        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="left-inner-box">
                Ready to take your love for chess to the next level by engaging in exciting competitions, meeting new opponents, and refining your strategies with the best campus players?<br><br>
                <button onclick="redirectToLogin()">Sign Up</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-box">
            <div class="right-inner-box">
                <div class="sub-box">
                    <div class="sub-feature-upper">
                        <img src="/images/profilepic.png" alt="Feature 1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="sub-feature-lower">
                        ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐<br>
                        "As a college chess player, I’ve been searching for a community like this for ages. Bringing masters together made me improve my skills like never before"
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="sub-box">
                    <div class="sub-feature-upper">
                        <img src="/images/profilepic.png" alt="Feature 2">
                    </div>
                    <div class="sub-feature-lower">
                        ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐<br>
                        "I never knew how much fun chess could be until I joined Chess Hive! It's the perfect place to improve your game, challenge players from other colleges, and stay up to date with upcoming tournaments."
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Chess Hive</p>
        </div>
        <nav class="social-links">
            <a href="#">Facebook</a> 
            <a href="#">Twitter</a>  
            <a href="#">Instagram</a>
        </nav>
    </footer>

    <script>
        function redirectToLogin() {
          window.location.href = "/signup";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>